Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a distorted world,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can we do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}CONCERT OF THE DAY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning off the AC.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting the track.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Vocaloid songs are pretty\Ndifficult to sing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:01:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your specialty is composing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So I really think we should find a vocalist\N who's a good match for your tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.56,0:01:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I already said no, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.94,0:01:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can't be helped then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.19,0:01:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just keep going with the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take out the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.41,0:01:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think it'd be better that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.71,0:01:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,22,738 FOLLOWERS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really want to go {\i1}that far{\i0},\Nit'll be a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}AIM FOR THE BUDOKAN!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:20.91,Title,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H0FFFFFF&\3c&H777777&\4c&HFFFFFF\i1\b1\fnSegoe Script\pos(1580,932)}ANTHEM OF THE\N OUTCASTS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how's your throat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It, uh, kinda got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru, Nina, come to the sauna. It's good for your throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...you're not gonna last long\Nif you're gonna be like this after every concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.93,0:03:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the good kind of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really lets that post-concert feeling sink in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Owie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, that was one mess of a concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really fun though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And Nina {\i1}really{\i0} went wild there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't exactly all\Nthat docile either, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And on drums, it's Pleia-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's mee!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I can't exactly use my real name, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta stay in character.\NThe super-cute JK, Pleia-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh, think I'm gonna get out now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, she's completely hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who, Nina?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to read you the comments from our concert's video.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's not Diamond Dust without Momoka."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"There's definitely more "rock" in her new group\N than in the new Diamond Dust."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, someone said Nina's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the audience definitely\Nprefers the old Diamond Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to ride that wave and start telling\Neveryone that the new Diamond Dust are fakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That they should support us instead because we're more like the original?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see how much followers they have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,20,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's going up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Remind me, how much do we have again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,500…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Business as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Writing songs, rehearsals, and concerts from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's our goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going to college in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking what {\i1}your{\i0} goal is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got out of the bath, let me relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I'm kinda curious too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you were a professional before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would someone like that suddenly\Nstart a band with a bunch of amateurs like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was wondering if you have\Nsomething specific you're aiming for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No general goals either?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, none.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.46,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Annoying, annoying, annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You got rice on your cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.26,0:06:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I try to have a serious discussion\N with her, she's always so, so-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're way too aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a bull seeing red.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Moo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way she'll be honest\N with us under that much pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a better idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly lead her into opening up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly and carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's called lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how she actually feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, what do {\i1}you{\i0} want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To beat Diamond Dust?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one high hurdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pros who already signed with a label.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Band goals"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.82,0:07:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Band how to become pros"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Becoming pros?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, finally got the spark huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we already\Ndecided on it or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted more info.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in my day, people from music labels used to\Ngo around venues likes ours
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to scout people, ask them for demos\Nor invite them for auditions, stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But these days, they mostly just reach out to whoever gets popular on the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is getting signed by a label that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.03,0:08:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can publish your music online,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but you need labels for the\Npromotion and collab opportunies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first you should get to where\NDiamond Dust were in their indie days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They got almost 10,000 followers back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they got noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's about numbers after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Followers are an indicator of a potential audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you have, the more offers you'll get.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}471 FOLLOWERS
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did... did it go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Watch the storm pass by{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The city is caught in a whirlwind of truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where should we let it lead?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we can smile upon arrival{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let us hold our hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not a dream{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"If nothing's going to come of it anyway, we're better off the way we are now."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"If we're going to get hurt,\Nwe might as well just stay like this."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're completely wrong\Nto think that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll still have to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, {\i1}that{\i0} sounds ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}AIM FOR BUDOKAN!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think it'll go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the most compatible people\Nsometimes fight and drift apart,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,while others without anything in common\N might just stay together for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But something tells me you'll get\Nalong pretty well with those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Gut feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have to clean up, so we probably won't have enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.63,0:10:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask if we could\Ndiscuss our stage outfits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But weren't you the one\Nwho made them last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.98,0:10:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I thought we could\Ngo for something cuter next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Something cuter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and by the way, can I pleease upload these photos of you to our socials?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oooh, nice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shining like a star!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This will definitely get us a ton of followers-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,ABSOLUTELY NOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were so into it\Nwhen we were taking them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you post your own mug instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I just thought our fans\N would appreciate some fanservice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if my grandma sees it, genius?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want more followers that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to be able to attract customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, let's all put on school uniforms
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and rebrand ourselves to\N Shin-Kawasaki Girls' High.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If Momoka-san wore a school uniform, it'd be like we're scamming people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl, that's a low blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kick your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that's actually going\Nto work, then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that exactly what the new\NDiamond Dust is doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll never even be on the same\Nplaying field if we can't go professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that we need a big audience, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When did we even start talking so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way we can beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And since when did we start\Ntalking about beating anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not holding a grudge against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.15,0:11:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't want to lose to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go shoving your daydreams\Nand personal circumstances on people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still don't want to lose to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I understand you and everything, but-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:11:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But suddenly throwing this going\Npro stuff at her is a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it'll be all smooth sailing\Njust because she already was a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't think we can beat Diamond Dust as we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate the idea of just giving up without trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not in the wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Medium without onions, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Medium for me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, two mediums and-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.95,0:12:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were musicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow us to introduce ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Rupa. And this is Tomo Ebizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been composing on\Nour own for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it got pretty popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So you two were behind it, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, so the reason you brought us here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a band duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- A complaint?\N- Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooooh, I know!\NWe're your 10,000th customers and-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty slow on the uptake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is she talking about a-?\N- Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,S-c-o-u-t-i-n-g.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Scouting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's scouting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Scouting who?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you stealing her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, dangit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We want all three of you to team up with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.73,0:13:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- No way.\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw your concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So we talked about it a bit,\Nand thought it'd be a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Girl, fix your record...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But can't really bring in a big audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and we don't have many followers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same boat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Though we did get offers from a few labels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.14,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But once we started discussing the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we realized what they had in mind wasn't\Nexactly the kind of music we wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They just wanted us to make things\N that would fill their pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That might be a bit harsh,\Nbut that's the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say they weren't\N a good match for Tomo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you came to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I saw your concert,\Nand it got me thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys definitely play exactly\N what you want, just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe we'll be able to you know, have a proper clash of opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's exactly the\Nvibe we were going for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina's definitely an expert when\Nit comes to clashing opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Come in.\N- Thanks for having us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn on the lights in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it here?...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just go running around in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- A lizard!\N- It's a gecko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're aiming for the Budokan, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Budokan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.78,0:15:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So what? Something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I never even thought of something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, how big is this Budokan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.47,0:15:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure do, I heard about it. And saw it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.56,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Country bumpkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from Sendai yourself, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're from Sendai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Kumamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm talking about the city in Miyagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.11,TLNote,,0,0,0,,{\an8}TL Note : There is another Sendai, which is a small village in the Kagoshima prefecture, deep in the countryside and much closer to Kumamoto where Nina is from. So basically Nina mistakenly thought they're fellow country bumpkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're close to it anyway,\Nwant to go see it up close?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.20,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, it's way too late for going out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:16:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now, seeing your goal up close will be good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,BUDOKAN
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If we manage to perform here someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If we really do it, we'll prove that we weren't the ones in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That we haven't lost to Diamond Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for the Budokan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call Momoka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you really that stupid?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who said we should get a bassist and a keyboardist!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But their goal is the Budokan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's basically the same as going professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think Momoka-san will just go along with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then what {\i1}should{\i0} we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I still want to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're at it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the only way you can\Nthink of, Miss Know-It-All?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What other ways are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought of something, didn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise not to call me a liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you, if you're not gonna\Ngo "it's called lying" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The mixing is well done, and the\Ntransitions are impressive as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Anddd, they're a bassist and a keyboardist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like the perfect opportunity to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What did they say about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They really really wanted-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd like to try a session this Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, then I'll keep you updated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's called lying!\N- That's called going in with a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did she say yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:18:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...not exactly, but she didn't say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just how I see it, but
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say Momoka-san has two halves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One half is fully absorbed in her music,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,giving it her all to create\Nsomething amazing of her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to see if her music\Ncan resonate with the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But the other half is a full-on realist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks of herself as having "dropped out\Nof the fight" when it comes to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She wonders if there's even any point\Nto taking it seriously again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That stuff doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she going to play with us or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel like she'll agree\Nif she likes our sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a musician through\Nand through after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.92,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have to start preparing now?\NSounds like a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What does she mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Less questions, more doing as I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.43,0:19:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A FEW DAYS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels good to play in a studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.98,0:19:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there's something wrong with this cable-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it real?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.37,0:19:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you take a picture with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan watches every episode\N at least three times while it's airing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She always cries at the ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No one asked you for the details...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, you're really lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.38,0:19:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Tendo Awa is known to prefer to keep\Nher distance from her admirers-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, {\i1}Awa?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Details. Now.\N- Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. I'm Rupa, a bassist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is Tomo, on synth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.28,0:19:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're the girls from the restaurant…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Order something other than a medium\Nwith a beer for once, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nice to meet you. I'm Kawaragi, a guitarist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And by that she means she's the great\N Momoka Kawaragi of Diamond Dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think I forgot about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are we playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we do the song from our concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with that,\Nbut can the new girls play it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we practiced a bit before you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna play it my way though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that okay with you?\N- Just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we won't know if we don't try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One, two, three, four.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amazing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's insane.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The city is caught in a whirlwind of truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.01,0:21:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where should we let it lead?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a distorted world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What can we do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We were wondering if\Nthey could join the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.54,0:21:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to prove that you aren't in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That your songs won't lose to theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.42,0:21:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The first step is to get noticed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They have an amateur division.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We send in a demo, we get selected to play,\Nwe go on stage, and get attention. That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we get offers from music labels?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.07,0:22:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, festivals are the playground of producers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So they'll definitely be on the lookout.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoping to find a diamond in the rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So there we'll-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Diamond Dust.
